    • Method Detail

      • update

        public void update()
            throws AlexandriaException
        Find files on the Context.searchPath that are not already indexed. Newly indexed files will only have their Config.DocumentMetadata.sourcePath and Config.DocumentMetadata.title set. The index will be saved after all matches are processed before throwing any exceptions that may have occurred during batch processing.
        Throws:
        AlexandriaException - Exception wrapping all exceptions thrown during document processing.

      • documentsMatched

        protected static Collection<Path> documentsMatched(Context context)
                                            throws AlexandriaException
        Find all files on Context.searchPath that match the configured include and exclude patterns.
        Parameters:
        context - Alexandria context containing information necessary to match files
        Returns:
        All matching files resolved as absolute using Context.configPath
        Throws:
        AlexandriaException - wrapper for any IOException thrown during conversion to make it integrate with BatchProcess
        See Also:
        PathFinder

      • documentsAlreadyIndexed

        protected static Collection<Path> documentsAlreadyIndexed(Context context)
        Converts Config.metadata documents into their source file paths for comparison to matched documents.
        Parameters:
        context - Alexandria context containing metadata index
        Returns:
        Document metadata paths resolved as absolute using Context.configPath

      • documentsNotIndexed

        protected static Collection<Path> documentsNotIndexed(Collection<Path> documentsMatched,
                                                      Collection<Path> documentsAlreadyIndexed)
        Compare to sets of paths to determine which have not been indexed. Both sets of Paths should have the same bases or they wont equate properly.
        Parameters:
        documentsMatched - Collection of matched documents.
        documentsAlreadyIndexed - Collection of metadata paths.
        Returns:
        List of all paths not already indexed, or empty list if no new documents need to be indexed.
